==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Undercoat
<hw>Un"der*coat`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
coat worn under another; a light coat, as distinguished from an
overcoat, or a greatcoat.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A growth of short hair or fur partially concealed by
a longer growth; <as>as, a dog's <ex>undercoat</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Underconduct</ent>⟦br⟧
